beer.beer_description:
Our friends at HPA called us up to take part in a collaboration series in which they invited breweries to make a beer to showcase a new hop product now available to brewers called LUPOMAX®.

We chose to make a nice clean American Wheat Beer to showcase LUPOMAX® using a couple of our favourite hop varieties (Citra and El Dorado) that play well together and would shine in a nice clean and fresh wheat beer.
